%p
  The Bike Index maintains a comprehensive list of biking related brands. If you want to get a list of brands that do biking things, you're in the right place.

%h3
  Query
%p
  Get information from a specific manufacturer. Query is case insensitive.

%article.code
  .code-label
    GET manufacturer with the name "surly"
  - request_url = api_v1_manufacturers_url(query: "surly")
  %pre
    :plain
      $.ajax({
        type: "GET",
        url: "#{request_url}",
        success: function(data, textStatus, jqXHR) {
          $('#manufacturers-query').text(data)
        }
      });

  .code-label
    Response
  %pre#manufacturers-query{ data: {url: request_url }}

%h3
  The full list
%p
  You can use this to with an #{link_to "autocomplete plugin", "http://twitter.github.io/typeahead.js/"} or improved select boxes. We use #{ link_to "Select2", "https://github.com/ivaynberg/select2"}.

%article.code
